I've spent almost only 1 and a half years in this school. 
met some people i know i wouldnt want to forget, made some friends and lost some too. 
i was a bit skeptical about re-doing yr 12 & 13 after finishing school back home, but now i wish i had came here earlier, i wish i had more time here, and i wish i had more chance to get to know a little more about everyone and everything here.
Or i wish i wasnt so shy, i wish i wasnt so anxious, i wish it was easier for me, i wish i could just make the most of my time here. But still, i wouldnt change a thing even if i could
